Package blue.mdc.event

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddEvent
    Add Event class create a pane and adds text fields to the pane asking for: Event Name Organization Name Advisor Transportation Number of Students in Organization Number of Students attending event Number of chaperones attending event Start Date and End Date Location Also it has a button to save the information to the database
    AddTraveler
    Add Traveler class create a pane and adds text fields to the pane asking for: Name Last Name MDC IDC Phone Email Address City Campus Zip Code Also it has a button to add contact information of the student, and a SAVE button to save the information to the database
    Event
    Event is a desktop application to help you make events easier.
    Intro
    Introduction to Event Application
    MainView
    Main View of Event Application
    Side
    Pane that represents the left blue Side bar of the Event Application.
